{"tid":1068940,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救] iPad Bootloop 開唔到機","createTime":"2019-03-19T14:57:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T02:28:49.000Z","uid":219266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b9dbc766a03bc8b8979b4418d9169df10ece071d","tid":1068940,"uid":219266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T14:57:25.000Z","msg":"之前更新完 iOS 之後冇叉電，第二晚返去睇部機冇曬電&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住叉返著佢就 Bootloop&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後分別試過入 Recovery 同 DFU 用 iTunes 回復原廠設定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但結果連 iOS 都洗唔到，會出 Error 9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知 Error 9 好似係連接問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我肯定唔係條 Lightning 線問題，因為本身用開 Apple 野用嚟叉電一切正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我試 iTunes 回復更新個陣，洗 iOS 通常會出到 Apple Logo 同條 Bar Run 緊<br />\n但洗洗下就會好似以下條片嘅 Bootloop 咁<br />\n出完 Apple Logo 下面唔知彈舊嘢出嚟，然後黑 Mon 再 Loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更新個陣就一彈果舊野即出 Error 洗唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日唔知做乜咁好彩，iTunes 洗 iOS 洗到落部機到，寫成功咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但一樣係 Bootloop&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有乜理由更新完 iOS 之後冇曬電<br />\n<br />\n各位大神有咩提議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://vimeo.com/325219429\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvimeo.com%2F325219429&d=pHv7ulxaPAPTUdGhwq1YMQxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=36428459\" target=\"_blank\">https://vimeo.com/325219429</a>"},{"pid":"c98b145b1387b0b330858333cab632787d0007f0","tid":1068940,"uid":219266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T14:59:49.000Z","msg":"Sorry for 1999<br />\n原 Po 可能有少少筆誤同打錯字<br />\n因為真係打得太急<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9273a9c82a2a244da3846a427156f0a37af2057a","tid":1068940,"uid":108893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T15:05:44.000Z","msg":"拎去蘋果啦 仲上黎問 你咩都試過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac8b9c8e55e3617cd14e18749b3bfd8e6db8f82b","tid":1068940,"uid":219266,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9273a9c82a2a244da3846a427156f0a37af2057a","tid":1068940,"uid":108893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T15:05:44.000Z","msg":"拎去蘋果啦 仲上黎問 你咩都試過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T16:03:52.000Z","msg":"試過去 Genius<br />\n佢咪又係搵個 iTunes 同我整<br />\n咁我去 Genius 做咩啫<br />\n<br />\n佢冇辦法就叫我交去整，不過都應該唔平<br />\n佢叫我寧願買過部咁話啦喎<br />\n<br />\n當刻心諗，Apple 啲嘢有冇咁化學"},{"pid":"81d3e40daa882576710bb3510b52821a85634f40","tid":1068940,"uid":26082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac8b9c8e55e3617cd14e18749b3bfd8e6db8f82b","tid":1068940,"uid":219266,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9273a9c82a2a244da3846a427156f0a37af2057a","tid":1068940,"uid":108893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T15:05:44.000Z","msg":"拎去蘋果啦 仲上黎問 你咩都試過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T16:03:52.000Z","msg":"試過去 Genius<br />\n佢咪又係搵個 iTunes 同我整<br />\n咁我去 Genius 做咩啫<br />\n<br />\n佢冇辦法就叫我交去整，不過都應該唔平<br />\n佢叫我寧願買過部咁話啦喎<br />\n<br />\n當刻心諗，Apple 啲嘢有冇咁化學"},"citedBy":1,